-- Samsung Loses First German Patent Case Against Apple in Mannheim Court
-- B y   K a r i n   M a t u s s e k
-- 2012-01-20T08:07:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-20/samsung-loses-first-german-case-against-apple-in-mannheim-court.html
Samsung Electronics Co. lost
a patent infringement suit against rival  Apple Inc. (AAPL)  at a court
in Mannheim,  Germany , today. The ruling is the first decision in
a group of patent cases the companies have filed against each
other in the country.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Karin Matussek in Berlin at 
